data.description:
Presenting a fantastic Old Aurora charmer: a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom brick home nestled on a corner lot. This property has been thoughtfully updated to provide modern comfort and style.

You'll discover an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The updated kitchen and bathrooms shine with stone and granite countertops, marrying aesthetics with functionality. Energy-efficient windows enhance the interior ambiance and contribute to Entergy cost savings. The home offers a spacious primary bedroom with large closets, ensuring ample storage. A new AC system guarantees year-round comfort and efficiency.

Outside, the generously sized backyard and patio are true gems. Accessible from the street through a double gate, it offers versatility and convenience. Sunshades provide a perfect retreat for outdoor relaxation and entertainment in any weather.

This property blends modern amenities with classic charm, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a comfortable and stylish living space. Don't miss your chance to call this wonderful house your home!
